New Order Notification
======================

Hello <%= @admin.name.presence || @admin.email %>,

A new order has been placed on Vinyl Saigon.

Order Details:
--------------
Order Number: <%= @order.order_number %>
Customer Name: <%= @order.name.presence || 'N/A' %>
Customer Email: <%= @order.email.presence || 'N/A' %>
Customer Phone: <%= @order.phone_number.presence || 'N/A' %>
Total Amount: <%= number_to_currency(@order.total_vnd, unit: "₫", format: "%n %u", precision: 0) %>
Payment Method: <%= @order.payment_method&.titleize || 'N/A' %>
Payment Status: <%= @order.payment_status.titleize %>
Shipping Method: <%= @order.shipping_method.titleize.gsub('_', ' ') %>
